.entry-header
About Us
Where Friends, Fun and Great Food Meet
Thirsty Turtle Seagrill opened its doors in Juno Beach in 1994 and the rest is history. We have been serving the South Florida area with our 4 different locations providing the best and freshest seafood you can find.
Our extensive menu is just the beginning as we not only offer great meals but good times.
We cater to both locals and tourists by ensuring everyone who dines with us has an unforgettable experience. From live entertainment to our wall of 60” TV screens there is always something going on here for you to enjoy with friends and family.
We have built our brand on proving friendly customer service, delicious food, and a place to be enjoyed by all crowds.
